    "description": "<br><br>Enjoy the prologue for Koboo: The Tree Spirit. An new take on action roguelike platformers drawing inspiration from the 2D souls-like combat from Dead Cells, the scale of Shadow of the Colossus and the enchanting world of Princess Mononoke. Master challenging combat, befriend woodland creatures and restore balance to the ancient ecosystem.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short and sweet experience with 20 minute runs<br></li><li>Difficult combat requires skillful movement and positioning<br></li><li>Unlock weapons and animal abilities to customize your build each run<br></li><li>Many accessibility and gameplay options<br></li><li>Plant your own garden in between battles<br></li><li>Full controller support</li></ul><br>Koboo: The Tree Spirit wouldn't be possible without the incredible support of our amazing Kickstarter community. Their passion and constructive feedback continue to shape the game, making it even better than we ever dreamed! You can follow our development and talk to us live on Discord anytime, we will respond as soon as possible.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thank you! ❤</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Jerome and Simon</h2>",
